>>3bdfd5ba-d221-46dd-9bec-ab3c98d97597
Nah its more fan-made decentralized version of 8chan than anything else.

Its not the official thing but its not a CIA or FBI inside job either. CodeMonkey just stated it was made by them and that's it. Doesn't mean its a honeypot its just fan-made.

>>51e84b0b-e041-404a-b2c5-00de8b92c3dc
Even if 8chan manages to return to the surface internet it won't be the same again.

Thanks to the recent shootings the feds will keep a close watch of 8chan and pressure globals, mods, and janitors to sanitize /b2/ and /pol/. Eventually Jim himself will cave and he'll eventually have Ron Watkins order globals/mods to sanitize the chans. Its the inevitable fate for chan boards that get too popular to become like 4chan.
